1985;;Anna Karenina;;American;;Simon Langton;;Jacqueline Bisset, Christopher Reeve, Paul Scofield, Ian Ogilvy;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anna_Karenina_(1985_film);;Tragic Anna Karenina leaves her cold husband for the dashing Count Vronsky in 19th-century Russia. The unfortunate series of events leave her hopelessly depressed.